{"type":"message","id":"1418ee92","parentId":"04a9c452","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:46:24.022Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:4637ce5f-71f1-4213-83c0-63508d6d599c task:4637ce5f-71f1-4213-83c0-63508d6d599c] 请调查并整理当前主流的 AI 音乐生成平台。\n\n要求：\n1. 搜索并列出主要的 AI 音乐生成平台（至少 10 个）\n2. 对每个平台，整理以下信息：\n   - 平台名称和官网\n   - 主要特点/功能\n   - 定价模式（免费/付费）\n   - 输出质量/风格特点\n   - 使用门槛（是否需要专业技能）\n\n3. 特别关注：\n   - 最热门/最受欢迎的平台\n   - 中文用户友好度\n   - 是否支持歌词生成\n   - 是否支持人声/演唱\n\n4. 按热度或推荐度排序\n\n5. 输出格式：整理成清晰的 Markdown 表格 + 简要文字说明\n\n搜索关键词建议：\n- \"AI music generation platforms 2024 2025\"\n- \"AI 音乐生成平台\"\n- \"Suno AI Udio alternatives\"\n- \"best AI song generator\"\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 3rd, 2026 — 4:46 PM (Asia/Shanghai)"}],"timestamp":1772527584020}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3714518","parentId":"1418ee92","timestamp":"2026-03-03T08:46:41.145Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户通过 cron 任务要求我调查并整理当前主流的 AI 音乐生成平台。这是一个研究任务，需要：\n\n1. 搜索网络获取最新信息\n2. 整理至少 10 个平台\n3. 提供详细信息（特点、定价、质量等）\n4. 特别关注中文用户友好度、歌词生成、人声演唱等\n5. 按热度排序\n6. 输出为 Markdown 表格 + 文字说明\n\n让我先进行网络搜索，获取最新的 AI 音乐生成平台信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来帮你调查当前主流的 AI 音乐生成平台。让我先进行网络搜索。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_14a54459f2e74afc9e35a90b","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"AI music generation platforms 2025 2026 best","count":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1852b8ad3b6c45a8b8f5efa1","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Suno AI Udio alternatives AI music generator","count":10}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_17a74c243e564741b52cde48","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"AI 音乐生成平台 2025 中文","count":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":26315,"output":202,"cacheRead":7424,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33941,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772527584021}}
